  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting to develop a Truth Commission in political crises context in Honduras</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project focus on supporting CSO efforts to implement a Truth Commission that seeks to contribute to dignify and restitute  human rights of victims and familiaries of the repression in the context of political crises in Honduras due to cuop.  This will be reached through the development of a process of opening the truth from the historical, political and social perspective. Some of the key activities includes investigation and documentation of cases, developping a comunication strategy, setting alliances with SEGIL and other international organizations  and   advocacy work to OEA, CIDH, UE, NNUU and others.</narrative>
  </description>
